data.content: Tu nombre es... ¡espera! ¡No puedo ver tu nombre! ¿Me lo podrías decir?
Can you tell me the days of the week in German?

Of course! Here are the days of the week in German:

- Montag (Monday)
- Dienstag (Tuesday)
- Mittwoch (Wednesday)
- Donnerstag (Thursday)
- Freitag (Friday)
- Samstag (Saturday)
- Sonntag (Sunday) 

Let me know if you need help with anything else!
